(3) Include criteria for a parolee to achieve early termination of and final
discharge from parole by the director of probation and parole.
SECTION 3. The department of correction is authorized to promulgate rules to
effectuate this act. The rules must be promulgated in accordance with the Uniform
Administrative Procedures Act, compiled in Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 4, Chapter 5.
SECTION 4. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
